Package com.xtructure.xneat.operators.impl

Class Summary
AbstractNEATOperator<D> AbstractNEATOperator implements the NEATOperator interface.
AddLinkMutateOperator AddLinkMutateOperator is a MutateOperator that attempts to connect a previously unconnected pair of nodes in the GeneMap of a Genome.
AddNodeMutateOperator AddNodeMutateOperator is a MutateOperator that attempts to "split" a link in the GeneMap of a NEATGenome with a new node.
AdjustAttributesMutateOperator AdjustAttributesMutateOperator is a MutateOperator that changes the values of fields in a GeneMap's genes, rather than it's topological configuration.

RemoveLinkMutateOperator RemoveLinkMutateOperator is a MutateOperator that removes a single link from a Genome's GeneMap.
